t: Ijrauat wa-qawa'id al-tahqiq fi al-hawadith al-bahriyah
Al-wajiz fi huquq al-milkiyah al-fikriyah : al-milkiyah al-sina'iya, al-milkiyah al-tijariyah
Al-huquq al-'ayniyah al-asliyah fi al-nizam al-sa'udi : haqq al-malkiyah wa-al-huquq al-mutafarri'ah 'anhu
Al-raqabah al-qadauiyah 'ala al-ta'dilat al-dusturiyah : dirasat muqaranah
Al-himayah al-dusturiyah lil-huquq al-biuiyah : dirasah muqaranah
Al-irhab al-duwali wa-al-muqawamah bi-al-isharah ila butlan asas qiyam al-kiyan al-israuili fi filastin min wijhat al-qanun al-dawli
Mustalahat al-sufiyah fi al-tafsir al-ishari, wa-yalihi, aqwal kibar al-'ulamau fi al-tasawwuf
Nizam al-'amal wa-al-tauminat al-ijtima'iyah fi al-mamlakah al-'arabiyah al-sa'udiyah : sharh, dirasah
Sulutat al-niyabah al-'ammah wa-maumuri al-dabt al-qadaui fi qanun al-ijrauat al-jinauiyah
